Weather details for Vagayskiy Rayon, on Saturday, August 10th:

The precipitation probability will change throughout the day between 0% and 5%. The highest chance for precipitation will be around 1 pm and the lowest probability around midnight. The dew point will range from 7°C up to a maximum value of 10°C around 8 am.
